Name: Touch Love
About the game: Summary This game is a line-type one-stroke drawing maze exploration game Specific gameplay: The player draws a line by dragging the block at the starting point with the mouse. The player's purpose is to find a path that does not repeat and connects all the blocks at one time in order to pass the level. After passing the level, you will also unlock the exquisite CG in the gallery!
